response.overview: Kate Middleton's outfits have always been in the public eye. We'll reveal her favourite labels and see how she styles for different occasions. Get to know her go-to fashion designers who include Catherine Walker, Jenny Packham and Alexander McQueen. We'll also find out what celebrities, stylists, and fashion writers think of her choices and ask them to reveal their favourites.
response.title: Kate Middleton's Wardrobe Secrets
